WEBVTT

00:00:00.120 --> 00:00:04.740
Hey, good morning, everybody. I have some

00:00:02.580 --> 00:00:06.600
things I want to share with you about

00:00:04.740 --> 00:00:11.820
what the Lord has shown me about the

00:00:06.600 --> 00:00:15.240
work and its escalation.

00:00:11.820 --> 00:00:18.119
Here we go. I was praying, and then

00:00:15.240 --> 00:00:22.020
the Lord showed me the massive storm

00:00:18.119 --> 00:00:24.840
again. I keep telling you all, I see

00:00:22.020 --> 00:00:27.000
the storm on the East Coast, and

00:00:24.840 --> 00:00:28.619
it was getting closer and closer.

00:00:27.000 --> 00:00:31.500
But this time when I was

00:00:28.619 --> 00:00:34.500
praying, the Lord showed me our

00:00:31.500 --> 00:00:37.140
American soldiers all in a single-file

00:00:34.500 --> 00:00:39.540
line,

00:00:37.140 --> 00:00:41.940
and they were headed toward the

00:00:39.540 --> 00:00:43.920
European area.

00:00:41.940 --> 00:00:46.440
The Lord told me there is

00:00:43.920 --> 00:00:48.960
going to be a massive draft, and they are

00:00:46.440 --> 00:00:53.519
going to draft all these people into the

00:00:48.960 --> 00:00:54.660
war. Suddenly,

00:00:53.520 --> 00:00:57.360
the devil

00:00:54.660 --> 00:01:00.779
takes me to Europe. I do not

00:00:57.360 --> 00:01:03.480
know what this devil was or

00:01:00.780 --> 00:01:06.540
what it represented necessarily, other

00:01:03.480 --> 00:01:09.420
than it was some

00:01:06.540 --> 00:01:11.580
kind of demonic spirit of war.

00:01:09.420 --> 00:01:14.400
He was in a pit,

00:01:11.580 --> 00:01:16.860
and in the pit, he had these massive

00:01:14.400 --> 00:01:19.619
chains on his arms, and he was

00:01:16.860 --> 00:01:24.000
chained down. Suddenly,

00:01:19.619 --> 00:01:25.560
an angelic being—it was a

00:01:24.000 --> 00:01:28.500
good one, an angel—came

00:01:25.560 --> 00:01:31.380
and took those chains

00:01:28.500 --> 00:01:33.780
off of that

00:01:31.380 --> 00:01:37.140
devil.

00:01:33.780 --> 00:01:40.500
He shot up out of the ground and

00:01:37.140 --> 00:01:42.900
was spinning like a top. He

00:01:40.500 --> 00:01:46.259
had these massive Viking

00:01:42.900 --> 00:01:50.060
horns on his head, and he had

00:01:46.259 --> 00:01:53.820
this fur with a

00:01:50.060 --> 00:01:56.280
leather sash across his chest.

00:01:53.820 --> 00:01:58.139
He had this fur, like a white-looking

00:01:56.280 --> 00:02:03.000
fur, polar-bear-looking

00:01:58.140 --> 00:02:05.939
outfit, like a Viking outfit.

00:02:03.000 --> 00:02:10.080
He started spinning and

00:02:05.939 --> 00:02:13.980
went inside of Vladimir Putin, and

00:02:10.080 --> 00:02:17.640
his whole countenance changed. He

00:02:13.980 --> 00:02:20.099
became energized, almost like he had

00:02:17.640 --> 00:02:22.440
lost his mind.

00:02:20.099 --> 00:02:24.540
It was weird, the way

00:02:22.440 --> 00:02:28.020
the Lord showed me. Suddenly, I

00:02:24.540 --> 00:02:31.679
want to show you—I have a picture here—so I could show you where I see

00:02:28.020 --> 00:02:35.400
the

00:02:31.680 --> 00:02:37.560
rocket. Do

00:02:35.400 --> 00:02:40.920
you have it on there, son?

00:02:37.560 --> 00:02:42.420
I saw a rocket come out of Russia and

00:02:40.920 --> 00:02:45.480
hit right here,

00:02:42.420 --> 00:02:48.238
right up in this area of Poland. It

00:02:45.480 --> 00:02:50.160
was a massive hit right next to here,

00:02:48.239 --> 00:02:51.420
in the

00:02:50.160 --> 00:02:53.340
corner.

00:02:51.420 --> 00:02:56.940
He was

00:02:53.340 --> 00:03:00.720
attacking this area with

00:02:56.940 --> 00:03:03.420
a massive bomb, but it was not

00:03:00.720 --> 00:03:05.760
anything that has ever been used

00:03:03.420 --> 00:03:08.940
before. Whenever I saw it happen,

00:03:05.760 --> 00:03:12.179
I said, "Oh no, he's using nuclear weapons."And

00:03:08.940 --> 00:03:14.340
the Lord said, "No, he is not. This is

00:03:12.180 --> 00:03:17.459
something that has never been used

00:03:14.340 --> 00:03:20.280
before on the Earth."He said, "This is a

00:03:17.459 --> 00:03:23.580
new technology."It was like it

00:03:20.280 --> 00:03:25.680
vaporized everybody, but it

00:03:23.580 --> 00:03:28.260
wasn't of the radiation and all this

00:03:25.680 --> 00:03:29.400
stuff.

00:03:28.260 --> 00:03:31.739
I've never seen anything like that

00:03:29.400 --> 00:03:33.300
before. The Lord said that

00:03:31.739 --> 00:03:36.900
nobody else had either; it's never been

00:03:33.300 --> 00:03:39.900
used before. Then

00:03:36.900 --> 00:03:44.840
I saw

00:03:44.900 --> 00:03:51.360
Turkey.

00:03:48.000 --> 00:03:55.080
From here over, there were these massive,

00:03:55.080 --> 00:04:01.799
humongous drums beating. I said, "Lord, what are

00:03:59.519 --> 00:04:04.080
they

00:04:01.799 --> 00:04:06.000
doing?"and

00:04:04.080 --> 00:04:09.060
He said, "They're going to

00:04:06.000 --> 00:04:10.860
join in and make ties.

00:04:09.060 --> 00:04:12.659
They're going to make some kind of

00:04:10.860 --> 00:04:15.120
financial agreements. There are going to be

00:04:12.659 --> 00:04:17.459
things that happen with them going in with

00:04:15.120 --> 00:04:19.858
Russia, and they're going to join in on

00:04:17.459 --> 00:04:21.600
the fight to help fund them and do

00:04:19.858 --> 00:04:24.719
things, and it's going to

00:04:21.600 --> 00:04:25.440
escalate even

00:04:24.720 --> 00:04:28.199
further."This

00:04:25.440 --> 00:04:32.699
thing got out of control.

00:04:28.199 --> 00:04:34.979
Then I was shown

00:04:32.699 --> 00:04:38.160
Israel. Iran

00:04:34.979 --> 00:04:40.620
and these

00:04:38.160 --> 00:04:41.880
other countries were all coming against

00:04:40.620 --> 00:04:44.220
Israel.

00:04:41.880 --> 00:04:46.259
But the United States

00:04:44.220 --> 00:04:49.800
turned our

00:04:46.259 --> 00:04:52.139
back. We turned our back, doing nothing.

00:04:49.800 --> 00:04:55.680
The Lord said, "This is what's going to

00:04:52.139 --> 00:04:57.440
happen during the Ezekiel 38 and

00:04:55.680 --> 00:04:59.699
39 War."People

00:04:57.440 --> 00:05:02.160
have always wondered, "Where's the

00:04:59.699 --> 00:05:04.440
United States in this?"We

00:05:02.160 --> 00:05:06.419
don't do anything. We don't help them.

00:05:04.440 --> 00:05:07.979
We just kind

00:05:06.419 --> 00:05:09.539
of watch, idly stand by and just watch.

00:05:07.979 --> 00:05:12.000
That's what I saw.

00:05:09.540 --> 00:05:16.680
Then I saw that

00:05:12.000 --> 00:05:20.820
because we betrayed Israel,

00:05:16.680 --> 00:05:24.060
we opened an attack for China to come in

00:05:20.820 --> 00:05:26.940
and get us. I saw China getting us.

00:05:26.940 --> 00:05:31.039
The surprise attack

00:05:33.180 --> 00:05:39.180
came as a dragon, and it looked like a

00:05:36.479 --> 00:05:41.820
red streaking dragon.

00:05:39.180 --> 00:05:44.400
Then the Lord showed me and He

00:05:41.820 --> 00:05:47.400
said, "Watch Hawaii."I could see Hawaii

00:05:44.400 --> 00:05:49.979
and all these F-16-looking fighter

00:05:47.400 --> 00:05:52.258
planes coming in, and they were just

00:05:49.979 --> 00:05:54.539
shooting missiles and going nuts on

00:05:52.259 --> 00:05:57.060
Honolulu and all these areas. I could

00:05:54.539 --> 00:05:59.400
see the main city there, Honolulu,

00:05:57.060 --> 00:06:01.500
Hawaii, and it was

00:05:59.400 --> 00:06:04.440
being annihilated

00:06:01.500 --> 00:06:06.539
with missiles and everything.

00:06:04.440 --> 00:06:09.120
Buildings were on fire and things were

00:06:06.539 --> 00:06:11.639
being shot down. It was a very

00:06:09.120 --> 00:06:13.740
sad situation because you could

00:06:11.639 --> 00:06:15.600
hear the sirens. I could hear

00:06:13.740 --> 00:06:17.580
some kind of air-raid sirens going off.

00:06:15.600 --> 00:06:19.139
People were running and screaming

00:06:17.580 --> 00:06:21.599
and trying to get away, but there was

00:06:19.139 --> 00:06:24.539
nowhere to escape because it's an island.

00:06:21.600 --> 00:06:26.160
People were

00:06:24.539 --> 00:06:30.419
fighting back and everything, but it was

00:06:26.160 --> 00:06:31.919
a serious issue. The virus,

00:06:30.419 --> 00:06:33.479
this is some of the things the Lord

00:06:31.919 --> 00:06:36.080
shows me. I don't always want to

00:06:33.479 --> 00:06:38.639
come on and be like a

00:06:36.080 --> 00:06:40.979
fearmonger or whatever you all would

00:06:38.639 --> 00:06:44.220
say, that he always has negative news. I'm

00:06:40.979 --> 00:06:46.800
just a watchman. I see and I pray, and

00:06:44.220 --> 00:06:49.620
the Lord shows me things to pray about

00:06:46.800 --> 00:06:51.539
and things that could come. Some

00:06:49.620 --> 00:06:52.560
things we can avert; some things we

00:06:51.539 --> 00:06:54.539
can't.

00:06:52.560 --> 00:06:56.460
When

00:06:54.539 --> 00:07:00.180
he told me about the virus

00:06:56.460 --> 00:07:03.419
coming, he showed me a massive wave.

00:07:00.180 --> 00:07:05.460
The wave came in and crashed the

00:07:03.419 --> 00:07:09.060
shore, and he told me this was the

00:07:05.460 --> 00:07:11.960
virus. Behind the virus

00:07:09.060 --> 00:07:13.979
was another massive,

00:07:11.960 --> 00:07:17.099
humongous wave.

00:07:13.979 --> 00:07:20.280
It was so big that it was

00:07:17.100 --> 00:07:23.099
frightening to look at.

00:07:20.280 --> 00:07:26.400
The Lord said as soon as

00:07:23.099 --> 00:07:30.000
this virus pulls back and starts to

00:07:26.400 --> 00:07:32.758
recede, another massive wave of a wake-up

00:07:30.000 --> 00:07:35.160
call will hit the earth. It's not about

00:07:32.759 --> 00:07:38.520
America; this is the

00:07:35.160 --> 00:07:39.840
world. He

00:07:38.520 --> 00:07:42.419
said there will be another wake-up call,

00:07:42.419 --> 00:07:49.460
another wave of whatever this is.

00:07:44.520 --> 00:07:53.580
But this time he showed me a number:

00:07:49.460 --> 00:07:57.900
350 million people would perish during

00:07:53.580 --> 00:07:59.460
whatever happens.

00:07:57.900 --> 00:08:02.520
I thought it would be another

00:07:59.460 --> 00:08:05.638
virus, like some kind of more serious

00:08:02.520 --> 00:08:07.380
thing, but I

00:08:05.639 --> 00:08:09.060
don't believe it is that. I believe it's

00:08:07.380 --> 00:08:11.639
something else. I don't know, and I don't want

00:08:09.060 --> 00:08:13.560
to assume. I just see and I don't

00:08:11.639 --> 00:08:15.900
want to add anything to it. I tell you

00:08:13.560 --> 00:08:17.940
exactly what I saw instead of saying,

00:08:15.900 --> 00:08:20.099
'I assume this,'because you

00:08:17.940 --> 00:08:22.259
get in a lot of trouble doing that. I

00:08:20.099 --> 00:08:24.180
just want to say exactly what I saw

00:08:22.259 --> 00:08:25.979
to you and tell you what the Lord

00:08:24.180 --> 00:08:28.680
showed me. I saw

00:08:25.979 --> 00:08:30.900
350 million people.

00:08:28.680 --> 00:08:33.020
Then the Lord showed me a vision.

00:08:30.900 --> 00:08:33.020
It was

00:08:33.479 --> 00:08:38.039
like

00:08:36.539 --> 00:08:41.458
a plane, and he said,

00:08:38.039 --> 00:08:43.679
'Like we plant, we sow, we reap.'He

00:08:41.458 --> 00:08:46.079
showed me people who are living

00:08:43.679 --> 00:08:48.959
Christians or

00:08:46.080 --> 00:08:51.720
pastors; if they're in hidden

00:08:48.959 --> 00:08:53.399
sin, they would be on the stage

00:08:51.720 --> 00:08:55.980
and just fall over dead like Ananias

00:08:53.399 --> 00:08:59.519
and Sapphira. It was going to be

00:08:55.980 --> 00:09:02.640
such a seed time acceleration of seed

00:08:59.519 --> 00:09:04.620
time and harvest of opening doors that

00:09:02.640 --> 00:09:06.600
the enemy comes in

00:09:04.620 --> 00:09:08.640
and just takes them out

00:09:06.600 --> 00:09:11.399
because of the open door they've

00:09:08.640 --> 00:09:13.319
caused. It was like

00:09:11.399 --> 00:09:16.440
an acceleration, a seedtime and

00:09:13.320 --> 00:09:18.060
harvest. It was very sad because

00:09:16.440 --> 00:09:19.920
there were people living in sin,

00:09:18.060 --> 00:09:22.560
pastors behind the pulpits and

00:09:19.920 --> 00:09:25.560
doing things. Christians living in an

00:09:22.560 --> 00:09:29.819
ungodly state were just dying.

00:09:25.560 --> 00:09:31.920
It wasn't just them;

00:09:29.820 --> 00:09:34.500
it was the world too. It was the people

00:09:31.920 --> 00:09:35.880
that weren't born again too.

00:09:35.880 --> 00:09:39.660
I'm trying to remember everything

00:09:39.660 --> 00:09:44.699
about that.

00:09:42.180 --> 00:09:46.739
Do you remember anything I'm leaving

00:09:44.700 --> 00:09:49.800
out? Because I talked about the people

00:09:46.740 --> 00:09:51.600
going home. It was very serious about all

00:09:49.800 --> 00:09:54.959
the people the Lord showed me going

00:09:51.600 --> 00:09:55.800
home. Thank you, Holy

00:09:54.959 --> 00:09:58.680
Ghost.

00:09:55.800 --> 00:10:03.599
He talked to me about an outpouring of

00:09:58.680 --> 00:10:06.599
finances. He showed me a small group

00:10:03.600 --> 00:10:08.820
of people. If you're praying,

00:10:06.600 --> 00:10:10.920
listening, keeping a

00:10:08.820 --> 00:10:12.600
fast life, and

00:10:10.920 --> 00:10:15.300
keeping your ear toward

00:10:12.600 --> 00:10:17.580
him,

00:10:15.300 --> 00:10:21.240
listening for his every word,

00:10:17.580 --> 00:10:24.860
he said there was

00:10:21.240 --> 00:10:28.680
going to be a supernatural

00:10:24.860 --> 00:10:30.980
outpouring of finances on a select few

00:10:28.680 --> 00:10:30.979
people,

00:10:31.220 --> 00:10:36.540
like inventions. I know how some of it

00:10:34.440 --> 00:10:39.060
happens, but I don't feel like I can talk

00:10:36.540 --> 00:10:41.279
about it.

00:10:39.060 --> 00:10:43.439
He showed me that the finances would come

00:10:41.279 --> 00:10:44.820
because he told

00:10:43.440 --> 00:10:46.380
me about the crash. There is going to be a

00:10:44.820 --> 00:10:48.360
massive crash;

00:10:46.380 --> 00:10:50.399
it's part of whenever

00:10:48.360 --> 00:10:52.680
they bring in the digital dollar and all

00:10:50.399 --> 00:10:55.620
the things. And I said, "Lord, how are these massive ministries going to happen and support

00:10:52.680 --> 00:10:58.260
these

00:10:55.620 --> 00:11:00.120
people?"This

00:10:58.260 --> 00:11:01.860
is something else he

00:11:00.120 --> 00:11:03.000
showed me because I was thinking about

00:11:01.860 --> 00:11:05.040
how people are going to get

00:11:03.000 --> 00:11:08.100
finances just to keep preaching the

00:11:05.040 --> 00:11:10.040
gospel. This is a big

00:11:08.100 --> 00:11:11.940
deal if another

00:11:10.040 --> 00:11:14.819
depression

00:11:11.940 --> 00:11:18.360
happens, similar to what occurred in the

00:11:14.820 --> 00:11:21.600
1920s and 1930s when the depression happened.

00:11:18.360 --> 00:11:24.200
He told me about supernatural provision.

00:11:21.600 --> 00:11:28.500
He said there will be an elite group

00:11:24.200 --> 00:11:31.440
that will walk in a

00:11:28.500 --> 00:11:34.560
financial outpouring that will bring in

00:11:31.440 --> 00:11:36.120
the money and help people.

00:11:34.560 --> 00:11:38.160
They'll be like a man with the pitcher in

00:11:36.120 --> 00:11:41.160
hand, helping out

00:11:38.160 --> 00:11:44.519
these ministries.

00:11:41.160 --> 00:11:46.620
I saw people because there was

00:11:44.519 --> 00:11:48.540
such a lack of food and supplies at

00:11:46.620 --> 00:11:49.980
the grocery stores.

00:11:49.980 --> 00:11:56.820
They will be at their dinner tables

00:11:52.860 --> 00:11:59.940
with empty pots, and the Lord showed me

00:11:56.820 --> 00:12:01.740
they will pray as a family around those

00:11:59.940 --> 00:12:05.880
empty pots. The Lord said, "I'm going

00:12:01.740 --> 00:12:08.100
to put food into those empty pots."I

00:12:05.880 --> 00:12:10.399
saw all kinds of

00:12:08.100 --> 00:12:12.600
soups and things that he provided

00:12:10.399 --> 00:12:14.940
supernaturally, just coming into those

00:12:12.600 --> 00:12:17.339
pots and filling them up every time they

00:12:14.940 --> 00:12:20.040
gathered around and gave him praise

00:12:17.339 --> 00:12:22.980
at the dinner table.

00:12:20.040 --> 00:12:25.620
Because the Bible says, "I never seen the

00:12:22.980 --> 00:12:27.420
righteous forsaken or their seed begging

00:12:25.620 --> 00:12:30.240
bread."And

00:12:27.420 --> 00:12:32.040
I believe with all my heart that

00:12:30.240 --> 00:12:34.860
even during all the drama that's going

00:12:32.040 --> 00:12:37.199
to take place before we go home—the

00:12:34.860 --> 00:12:41.220
birthing pains that are manifested on

00:12:37.200 --> 00:12:43.920
this Earth—we will see a supernatural

00:12:41.220 --> 00:12:46.560
provision just like the children of

00:12:43.920 --> 00:12:48.479
Israel had in the desert when he

00:12:46.560 --> 00:12:50.880
came in with the manna

00:12:48.480 --> 00:12:52.680
and took care of them with the quail. He

00:12:50.880 --> 00:12:55.200
always provided. He provided the twelve

00:12:52.680 --> 00:12:57.540
baskets,

00:12:55.200 --> 00:12:59.279
the fishes, and the loaves. He took care

00:12:57.540 --> 00:13:01.980
of them. He's going to take care of us.

00:12:59.279 --> 00:13:04.139
He's not going to let us go without.

00:13:01.980 --> 00:13:05.399
But you're going to have to be pushing into

00:13:04.139 --> 00:13:07.079
him. You're going to have to have a

00:13:05.399 --> 00:13:10.740
relationship with him. You're going to

00:13:07.079 --> 00:13:12.660
have to have a sin-free

00:13:10.740 --> 00:13:15.360
lifestyle as much as possible, living

00:13:12.660 --> 00:13:17.399
holiness. I'm not talking about how

00:13:15.360 --> 00:13:20.399
you can't do nothing.

00:13:17.399 --> 00:13:23.399
I'm talking about not living in

00:13:20.399 --> 00:13:26.519
compromise and sin. So you've got to live in

00:13:23.399 --> 00:13:27.720
a relationship where you're on fire

00:13:26.519 --> 00:13:28.860
for God and we're all preaching the

00:13:27.720 --> 00:13:31.139
gospel. And I'm telling you, he's going to

00:13:28.860 --> 00:13:33.120
take care of you. The Lord showed me—I

00:13:31.139 --> 00:13:36.060
want to get this documented because

00:13:33.120 --> 00:13:38.639
we're almost there.

00:13:42.060 --> 00:13:45.359
I'll tell one more thing here

00:13:43.500 --> 00:13:48.540
because he keeps reminding me of things.

00:13:45.360 --> 00:13:50.700
In

00:13:50.700 --> 00:13:55.019
2022,

00:13:55.019 --> 00:14:02.040
I had an angelic visitation in a dream.

00:13:57.839 --> 00:14:07.139
And in my dream, the angel told me, 'Great

00:14:02.040 --> 00:14:10.319
judgment is coming in 569 days.'And I

00:14:07.139 --> 00:14:13.440
asked the angel, 'What is the judgment?'and

00:14:10.320 --> 00:14:16.079
he said to me, 'I cannot tell

00:14:13.440 --> 00:14:18.779
you. You will have to pray this out. The

00:14:16.079 --> 00:14:21.660
Lord tells me you will have to pray this

00:14:18.779 --> 00:14:24.180
out in the spirit, and he will show

00:14:21.660 --> 00:14:28.439
you and give you revelation of this.'So

00:14:24.180 --> 00:14:31.859
I saw on the counter

00:14:28.440 --> 00:14:33.540
510 days. October 2nd is what

00:14:31.860 --> 00:14:36.180
the date came to.

00:14:33.540 --> 00:14:39.180
And so

00:14:36.180 --> 00:14:40.439
it was during Yom Kippur and Rosh Hashanah

00:14:39.180 --> 00:14:43.260
of last year.

00:14:40.440 --> 00:14:45.420
And the Lord told me whenever we got

00:14:43.260 --> 00:14:49.019
close to that timeframe, he said, 'I'm

00:14:45.420 --> 00:14:52.439
extending the timeframe and giving more

00:14:49.019 --> 00:14:55.440
time for repentance. I'm going to give more

00:14:52.440 --> 00:14:58.920
time. I'm pushing this back. I'm going to

00:14:55.440 --> 00:15:02.399
give the people more time.'I

00:14:58.920 --> 00:15:04.800
think I'll end it there. I have

00:15:02.399 --> 00:15:06.480
another video; keep watching. I

00:15:04.800 --> 00:15:08.639
just saw something else—he showed

00:15:06.480 --> 00:15:10.500
me in a vision right then, and I

00:15:08.639 --> 00:15:12.420
just saw something. So I'm going to

00:15:10.500 --> 00:15:15.860
tell you in another video what he showed

00:15:12.420 --> 00:15:15.860
me. All right, have a blessed day.

